229     */
230    public function updateFolder(): void
231    {
232        // Determine the appropriate folder based on status and user assignment
233        $folderType = match ($this->status) {
234            self::STATUS_ACTIVE => $this->user_id ? 1 : 2, // Assigned or Unassigned
235            self::STATUS_PENDING => 2, // Unassigned
236            self::STATUS_CLOSED => 4, // Deleted/Closed
237            self::STATUS_SPAM => 30, // Spam
238            default => 2, // Unassigned as fallback
239        };
240
241        // Find the appropriate folder
242        $folder = Folder::where('mailbox_id', $this->mailbox_id)
243            ->where('type', $folderType)
244            ->when($folderType === 1 && $this->user_id, function ($query) {
245                return $query->where('user_id', $this->user_id);
246            })
247            ->first();
248
249        if ($folder) {
250            $this->folder_id = $folder->id;
251            $this->save();
252        }
253    }
